7	
8	/* PAGE WRAPPER
9	   Full viewport width — the bg-art layer (.pdpBg) inherits this so the
10	   line arts can sit naturally at the screen edges instead of being clipped
11	   at a 1320px content cap. Inner content blocks (.crumbs, .productGrid,
12	   .craftStrip, .similarWrap) are individually max-width'd to keep reading
13	   widths comfortable. */
14	.pdp {
15	  width: 100%;
